MosquitoAlertBCN Insights: Week Ahead

This report is updated automatically each day to highlight key insights from the MosquitoAlertBCN platform.

City-Wide Trends

During the next 7 days, we estimate the mean VRI in Barcelona will be 0.21 and the maximum will be 0.49, occuring on September 30. Figure 1 shows the mean and maximum values estimated for each day.

Figure 1: Estimated city-wide VRI during next 7 days. Red line indicates maximum values each day; blue indicates means.

Figure 2 shows mean VRI estimates for each of Barcelonas districts. The district with the highest estimated mean VRI is Eixample, with a value of 0.29. The means, however, mask a great deal of spatial variation within districts.
